quran[3]{c,v,t,f}:
  114,4,"níbi aburú (Èṣù) oníròyíròyí, olùsásẹ́yìn (fún ẹni tó bá ń dárúkọ Allāhu. {1}",footnotes:1:[Ọ̀kan pàtàkì nínú àǹfààní àti oore tí ó wà nínú ath-thikār ṣíṣe ni pé, Èṣù àti àwọn ọmọ ogun rẹ̀ yóò máa sá sẹ́yìn fún ẹni tí ó bá ń ṣe ath-thikār ní gbogbo ìgbà. Kí á sì rántí wí pé, ọ̀kan pàtàkì jùlọ nínú ohun tí mùsùlùmí yóò máa fi ṣe ath-thikār ni kíké al-Ƙur’ān alápọ̀n-ọ́nlé ní ojoojúmọ́ ní díẹ̀ díẹ̀. Lẹ́yìn náà ni àwọn gbólóhùn ath-thikār èyí tí ó wà nínú ẹ̀gbàwá hadīth Ànábì - kí ìkẹ́ àti ọlà Allāhu máa bá a -.]
  114,5,"(Èṣù ni) ẹni tí ó ń kó ròyíròyí sínú àwọn ọkàn ènìyàn."
  114,6,"(Èṣù náà) wà nínú àwọn àlùjànnú àti àwọn ènìyàn.”"